In re Application of Black Fork Wind Energy, L.L.C. 2017-0412 Supreme Court of Ohio. June 13, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On intervening appellee's motion to dismiss. Motion denied.

O'Donnell, J., dissents.

Fischer and DeWine, JJ., dissent and would defer ruling on the motion to dismiss until the case is submitted on the merits.
